title: Roman Steblo website
text:
Roman Steblo is a political science student from Ukraine, struggling to theoretyzing, analysis of social life and victory over klyata rusnya. Topics of interest: governance, theory of modernization, nationalism in global world, security and defence sector.
Home city: Odesa, Ukraine.
Alma-mater: National University of Kyiv-Mohyla Academy.
Articles:

Moments of madness: the impact of contentious politics on the development of civil society in Ukraine.
Will the defense order be fulfilled?
